ℹ️ About Kraken Reels

Kraken Reels Charter Services delivers the best deep sea fishing experience out of Orange Beach, Alabama. Led by Captain Jon Ray and his experienced crew, every trip is a fishing adventure tailored to your needs — from family-friendly nearshore runs to adrenaline-filled offshore expeditions.

Operating out of Reel Surprise Marina in Orange Beach, Kraken Reels runs a 47-foot Sports Fisherman and a 30-foot Robalo Center Console, both equipped with state-of-the-art electronics, federal permits, and everything you need for a trophy day on the water.

Perfect For: Families, bachelor parties, corporate outings, experienced anglers, or first-timers looking for an unforgettable day on the Gulf of Mexico.

✨ What’s Included on Every Trip
✅ Professional rods & reels
✅ Live & dead bait
✅ Tackle & lures
✅ Fishing license (federal)
✅ Catch cleaning & filleting
✅ Water & ice

✅ Up to 6 guests

🎣 Charter Trips & Pricing
5-Hour Nearshore Trip Family Friendly
Calm waters just miles off the coast. Target vermillion snapper, triggerfish, red grouper, Spanish mackerel, king mackerel, and bonita. Perfect for families and beginners.
$1,000
6-Hour Deep Sea Trip Popular
Head 8–15 miles offshore for a balanced inshore/offshore experience. Target red snapper, grouper, amberjack, king mackerel, and blackfin tuna.
$1,350
8-Hour Offshore Adventure
Adrenaline-filled offshore trip, 40+ miles out. Target wahoo, tuna, red snapper, amberjack, king mackerel, and sharks. The full deep sea experience.
$1,800
20+ Hour Overnight Expedition Trophy
The ultimate fishing adventure — overnight on the Gulf. Chase yellowfin tuna, wahoo, swordfish, and blue marlin. For serious anglers seeking trophy catches.
Call
